<section>
  <h2>What's Included</h2>

  <h3>Data Attributes</h3>
  <ul>
    <li><a href="/docs/attributes/data-lorem/"><code>data-lorem</code></a> &mdash; fill any element with placeholder text (words, sentences, headings, list items). Supports Latin, CJK, Arabic, and Cyrillic corpuses.</li>
    <li><a href="/docs/attributes/data-mock/"><code>data-mock</code></a> &mdash; placeholder images, avatars, and media containers with configurable dimensions and styles.</li>
  </ul>
</section>

